Class IsIterableWithSize<E>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.hamcrest.Matcher<Iterable<E>>, org.hamcrest.SelfDescribing

    public class IsIterableWithSize<E>
extends org.hamcrest.collection.IsIterableWithSize<E>
    Does the Iterable has a given size?

    The matcher first checks if the given Iterable is a Collection (to get some speedup by using the Collection.size() method, otherwise iterates all the elements to get the size of the Iterable.

    Since:
    version 0.1 for JDK7
